ListInfo.Name: API - Demo
ListInfo.Description: A list of APIs with their URLs, specifications, and short descriptions for demo and testing purposes.
ListInfo.Instructions:
A list of APIs with their URLs, specifications, and short descriptions for demo and testing purposes. List Structure: Key - API Base URL Value - URL to API Specification (JSON or YAML) Comment - Short description of API service.
Special instructions for processing: 1. Retrieve the API from the list. 2. Use the specification URL to fetch and parse the API specification. 3. Based on the specification, call the appropriate endpoint in the API to get the output.
